This directory contains the available HOWTOS/FAQs translations to spanish till 
now; there are more documents on the job.

Here are the following servers/mailing lists whose contents are related with
translations; LuCAS is aimed to guides, while INSFLUG are to Howtos & FAQs. 

FTP:
	ftp://ftp.insflug.nova.es/
	ftp://ftp.infor.es/pub/LuCAS

WWW:
	http://www.insflug.nova.es/
	http://www.infor.es/LuCAS/

MAILING LISTS:

